00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:53.572
Tarn Adams is actually the
author of "Dwarf Fortress."

00:26:53.572 --> 00:26:56.030
"You activate bugs and little
parts of the code from eight,

00:26:56.030 --> 00:26:58.840
six years ago where you just
didn't balance the numbers,

00:26:58.840 --> 00:27:00.030
because it didn't matter."

00:27:00.030 --> 00:27:02.700
